title: Pattern Color Gradient Wallpaper-7

creator: Style-7
descriptionHtml:
Beautiful soothing color gradient wallpaper for the Home screen based on pattern and two colors. Using 160 patterns and any two colors, you can create an almost endless amount of unique variant of images for you taste. Experiment with colors and patterns and create light, dark, soft or contrast wallpapers.
All settings are made in a visual style: as you see as you get, which is very convenient.
Color gradient wallpaper are practically not boring, as you can quickly change their appearance by preferences.

Features:
* Select any of 160 templates. You can slowly review them all or quickly switch to any;
* A special color selector allow you to quickly and accurately adjust a desired color;
* You can swap two colors by one tap to see the result;
* Select depth of smooth. At low depth, you get an interesting image with fragments where you can see areas of solid color. At high depth you get a nice smooth image;
* Image quality does not depend of screen size;
* Support for landscape and portrait orientations;
* Color gradient wallpaper for high resolution screens without loss of quality;
* Color gradient wallpaper for HD and 4K screens;
* Set wallpaper on the Home screen and lock screen (may not be supported by some devices) by one tap;
* Fast and handy change of preferences;
* If you are tired of gradient, then you can set a solid color wallpaper. To do this, just select two the same colors.
